snippet.title: 🔴 LIVE | MPL PH S15 | FILIPINO - Playoffs Day 2
snippet.description:
This is Day 2 of the MPL PH S15 Playoffs. After 10 long games in the 1st day of the playoffs, there's sure to be more action!

First up, it's the Trailblazers of the New Era, the big match itself, the all-star showdown, Aurora Gaming vs Onic Philippines, the rematch of the Season 14 Grand Finals, who will book their spot in the upper bracket finals?

On the 2nd game of the day, we will see the Clash of the Titans, Team Liquid Philippines, tournament favourites going up against a familar foe in Team Falcons.

4 Teams, 2 heated match-ups. This is MPL PH.

Match Schedule:
 ⚔️ 3pm: RORA vs. ONIC (Bo5)
 ⚔️ 7pm: TLPH vs. FLCN (Bo5)
 
 Catch you at the land of dawn!
 
 #MPLPH #MPLPhilippines #MLBB #MobileLegendsBangBang #EsportsPH #MPLPHSeason15
